The paper deals with record linkage, which is a common problem in database management (cs.DB). The algorithm proposed in the paper involves processing large datasets efficiently, which is a common problem in information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The algorithm also involves handling data quality issues, which is a common problem in data science (cs.DS) and cybersecurity (cs.CR).
